I hope it will , indeed ! '' she breathed . 
'' Er yes , Cyril told me , '' admitted Marie . 
Didn't like it , I suppose eh ? '' she queried shrewdly . 
N no , I'm afraid he didn't very well . 
He said she'd be one more to be around . 
'' There , what did I tell you ? '' dimpled Billy . 
The man lifted his hat and waved it gayly , baring a slightly bald head to the sun . 
It's Uncle William bless his heart ! '' cried Billy . 
