She turned to Cyril with outstretched hand . 
Oh , yes , Marie's coming , '' she smiled in answer to the quick shifting of Cyril's eyes to the hall doorway . 
And Aunt Hannah , too . 
'' And Mary Jane ? '' demanded William , a little anxiously Will's getting nervous , '' volunteered Bertram , airily . 
He wants to see Mary Jane . 
