And to think of my letting you stand in line for a twenty five cent admission ! '' she scorned . 
Nonsense ! '' laughed Billy . 
It didn't hurt me any more than it did you . 
Come ! '' in looking about for a quick something to take her guest's attention , Billy's eyes fell on the manuscript copy of her new song , bearing Arkwright's name . 
